# AI Cake Studio — MVP Build Order (Feature-First Thinking)

---

## The Core Question: What Makes This Feature SHIPPABLE?

A user visits → designs a cake → gets real AI images → does something with it.

If any link in this chain is broken, **the feature cannot ship.**

