## MVP Build Order — By What Blocks Shipping

| # | What | Why It's This Priority | Blocked Without It |
|---|------|----------------------|-------------------|
| **1** | **AI Generation + Image Storage** | This IS the feature. Without real images, there's nothing to ship. Everything else is supporting infrastructure. | The entire product. Mock designs = demo, not product. |
| **2** | **Quota & Credits** | You're spending real money per generation (₹3–6 per image). Without quota, one user can bankrupt you in an hour. Ships same day as generation. | Financial safety. Cannot go live without it. |
| **3** | **Rate Limiting** | Even with quota, a user can spam 3 requests in 1 second. Need basic throttle. Tiny code, massive protection. | DDoS / abuse protection. 50 lines of code but critical. |
| **4** | **Real OTP** | Current mock OTP means anyone types any 6 digits and gets in. Quota is meaningless if auth is fake. | Auth integrity. Quota is bypassable without real OTP. |
| **5** | **Generation Ledger** | User generates → refreshes page → designs gone forever. Must persist. Also needed for "My Designs" and cost tracking. | User experience. Designs must survive page refresh. |
| **6** | **Order Handoff** | User has a design they love. Now what? Without a next step, the feature is a toy, not a business tool. | Revenue. This is where money comes from. |

**After these 6 → the feature is LIVE and EARNING.**

